trigger.name: AntMiner L3 Hashrate information not available on {HOST.NAME}

trigger.expression: (({AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Temp1.min(15m)}>{$TEMP_LOW} or {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Temp2.min(15m)}>{$TEMP_LOW} or {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Temp3.min(15m)}>{$TEMP_LOW} or {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Temp4.min(15m)}>{$TEMP_LOW}) and {AntMiner L3:icmpping.last()}=1)
trigger.recovery_expression: (({AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Temp1.last()}<{$TEMP_LOW} or {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Temp2.last()}<{$TEMP_LOW} or {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Temp3.last()}<{$TEMP_LOW} or {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Temp4.last()}<{$TEMP_LOW}) and {AntMiner L3:icmpping.last()}=1)
trigger.name: AntMiner L3 High temp on {HOST.NAME}

trigger.expression: {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Fan_num.last()}=0 and {AntMiner L3:icmpping.last()}=1 and ({AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Elapsed.last()} = {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Elapsed.prev()} and {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.Elapsed.last()}>0)
({AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.URL1.str({$URL1})}=0 or {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.URL2.str({$URL2})}=0 or {AntMiner L3:AntMinerL3.URL3.str({$URL3})}=0) and {AntMiner L3:icmpping.last()}=1
trigger.name: "" URL! {HOST.NAME}
